	(text "TODO:\n* Consider adding more capacitance to power regulators\n* Analog input and output gain stages\n* Decide whether this is a dev board or integrated\n   - if the former, is designed specifically for Eurorack signals?\n* Connect ADC pins\n* Add voltage reference for gain stages"
